 2019-02752019-04-05,  ,  ,  ECCC, 
ActHeritage Railway Stations Protection Act
SubjectAlterations to the VIA Rail Canada railway station in Ottawa, Ontario
PrecisOrder authorizing VIA RAIL CANADA to undertake alterations to the main concourse, east and west service wings, and east, west and south facades, at its railway station located at 200 Tremblay Road, Ottawa, Ontario, in order to protect and preserve the heritage character of the station.
